{
  "stem": "3658.2",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And that's the camp where I stayed till most of-- till the-- till '45.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "From '44 to '45, I stayed in Gusen II.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And Gusen II was just the end of the-- people that used to come from other camps told us that this is the worst camp that they've been.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And there are people that have been in the camps for years over a period.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "In fact, there's some people here I met that have been there too.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There, we were working in-- they took us to work with dogs on a-- on a-- on a-- in a place underground, in-- in a-- they call it in a-- what it-- where they were-- sort of you went into an underground and you were shoveling things on a belt--",
      "word_count": 50
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "A mine.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In a mine.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That's it, thank you.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "A mine.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And-- and that was a terrible camp.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They were beating and belting us.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Anyway, it was just terrible.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And hanging people in front of you to show you, if anybody escaped-- which some of them escaped-- what they did.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we all had to watch.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Whenever there's somebody that came back, you have to watch the punishment.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But you couldn't, because the wires were electrified too, you know, all around us, so we couldn't-- we couldn't move.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "To escape.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And when they took us to work in the mines, they took us with dogs.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So you can imagine.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We couldn't walk fast.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We were hungry.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We had no food.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The food was just a piece of bread and-- for everybody, and a [? bit of ?] soup, which was-- which was [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] like-- oh, you couldn't.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It was with stones and with everything.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
